@model HomeRent.Models.Administration.AmenityAdminModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Добавяне на удобство";
}

<section class="py-4" style="background-color: #fff;">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="d-flex justify-content-center">
            <ol class="breadcrumb bg-white">
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="AdminDashboard" asp-action="Index" style="color: #1563DF;">Администраторски панел</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item active" style="color: #1563DF;"><a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Amenities" asp-action="All"> Удобства</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page" style="color: #1563DF;"> Добавяне</li>
            </ol>
        </nav>

        <h2 style="color: #1563DF;">
            @ViewData["Title"]
        </h2>

    </div>
</section>

<div class="text-center my-3">
    <p>Добавете ново удобство, за да подобрите обявите за имоти. Осигурете ясно име и клас на иконата за удобството, за да бъде лесно разпознаваемо и полезно за категоризацията на имотите.</p>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="card mx-auto shadow" style="max-width: 500px;">
        <div class="card-body">
            <form method="post">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="Name" class="form-label">Наименование</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="Name" name="Name" asp-for="Name" placeholder="Въведете наименование">
                    <span asp-validation-for="Name" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="IconClass" class="form-label">Клас на иконата</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="IconClass" name="IconClass" asp-for="IconClass" placeholder="Въведете клас на иконата">
                    <span asp-validation-for="IconClass" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-4">
                    <button type="submit" class="tf-btn primary me-2">Запази</button>
                    <a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Amenities" asp-action="All" class="tf-btn btn-line">Отказ</a>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>